    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! You know those rare finds that make you do a double-take? Well, this is definitely one of them. I\u2019ve absolutely babied this beauty since the day I brought her home\u2014she\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed, and honestly, she still looks and smells like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s truly a pristine ride that drives as smooth as silk. I\u2019m looking for a good home for her, someone who appreciates a car that's been cared for with a little extra soul. Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
