    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in mechanical synergy, presenting in absolute showroom condition. The S54 power plant pulls with surgical precision, featuring a fully addressed VANOS system with Beisan components and a reinforced subframe to eliminate the chassis\u2019s factory Achilles heel. Rod bearings were proactively swapped for VAC treated units, ensuring the bottom end is bulletproof for high-RPM pulls. The suspension geometry has been optimized with custom-valved coilovers for neutral turn-in and zero body roll. Every bushing has been replaced with high-durometer polyurethane for a tactile, connected road feel without the NVH of a track car. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example with crisp throttle response and rifle-bolt gear engagement. Meticulously sorted and mechanically flawless.",
      "price": 44800.0,
